&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re on the look-out for a highly motivated and multi-skilled Accounts Assistant to join the Finance Team at our East Grinstead hospital on a bank contract.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll love to organise - maintaining accurate financial records in a timely manner. Assisting with the daily processing of the purchase ledger, you&#39;ll cross check the purchase order against goods received and invoices. Able to meet deadlines, you&#39;ll ensure all month-end requirements are met. You&#39;ll enjoy working with a range of suppliers and other departments and delight in the smooth running of the Finance office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
